### 4.2 Component Details

#### Data Sources
- System metrics (CPU, RAM, Disk via `psutil`)
- Network traffic (packet capture via `scapy`)
- Windows Event Logs (via `pywin32`)
- File system changes (via `watchdog`)
- External threat intelligence (AbuseIPDB API)

#### Log Collectors
- [system_logs.py](file:///d:/project/Sentinel/Sentinel_level8/Sentinel_Level8_Enterprise%20-%20Copy/c2_core/collectors/system_logs.py) — OS event logs
- [network_stats.py](file:///d:/project/Sentinel/Sentinel_level8/Sentinel_Level8_Enterprise%20-%20Copy/c2_core/collectors/network_stats.py) — Network interface statistics
- [system_info.py](file:///d:/project/Sentinel/Sentinel_level8/Sentinel_Level8_Enterprise%20-%20Copy/c2_core/collectors/system_info.py) — Hardware/OS information
- [network_monitor.py](file:///d:/project/Sentinel/Sentinel_level8/Sentinel_Level8_Enterprise%20-%20Copy/c2_core/collectors/network_monitor.py) — Active connections

#### Detection Engine
- **Rules Engine** ([rules_engine.py](file:///d:/project/Sentinel/Sentinel_level8/Sentinel_Level8_Enterprise%20-%20Copy/c2_core/detection/rules_engine.py)): Threshold-based alerting (CPU > 85%, Memory > 90%) with 30-second cooldown
- **Anomaly Engine** ([anomaly_engine.py](file:///d:/project/Sentinel/Sentinel_level8/Sentinel_Level8_Enterprise%20-%20Copy/c2_core/detection/anomaly_engine.py)): Placeholder for ML-based anomaly detection

#### AI Decision Engine
- **Analyst** ([analyst.py](file:///d:/project/Sentinel/Sentinel_level8/Sentinel_Level8_Enterprise%20-%20Copy/ai_brain/ai/analyst.py)): Hybrid keyword scoring + Ollama LLM analysis
- **Traffic Model** ([traffic_model.py](file:///d:/project/Sentinel/Sentinel_level8/Sentinel_Level8_Enterprise%20-%20Copy/ai_brain/ai/traffic_model.py)): Isolation Forest with online retraining
- **Predictive Engine** ([predictive_engine.py](file:///d:/project/Sentinel/Sentinel_level8/Sentinel_Level8_Enterprise%20-%20Copy/ai_brain/ai/predictive_engine.py)): MITRE ATT&CK graph traversal
- **Hunter AI** ([hunter.py](file:///d:/project/Sentinel/Sentinel_level8/Sentinel_Level8_Enterprise%20-%20Copy/ai_brain/ai/hunter.py)): Automated threat investigation with hypothesis-verdict loop

#### Alerting System
- WebSocket broadcast to all connected UI clients at 1Hz
- Discord webhook notifications via [active_defense.py](file:///d:/project/Sentinel/Sentinel_level8/Sentinel_Level8_Enterprise%20-%20Copy/soar_engine/active_defense.py)
- Redis Pub/Sub for cross-service event distribution
- Incident auto-creation for CRITICAL severity alerts

#### Dashboard/UI
- 11 dedicated pages built in React + TypeScript
- Real-time charts, traffic maps, and threat analytics
- Firewall management with panic mode toggle
- SIEM log viewer with filtering
- Agent monitoring (Nodes page)

#### Database/Storage
- **SQLite** ([sentinel_siem.db](file:///d:/project/Sentinel/Sentinel_level8/Sentinel_Level8_Enterprise%20-%20Copy/sentinel_siem.db)): SIEM log storage with blockchain integrity
- **SQLite** ([sentinel.db](file:///d:/project/Sentinel/Sentinel_level8/Sentinel_Level8_Enterprise%20-%20Copy/sentinel.db)): Application database (agents, incidents, audit logs)
- **SQLite** ([incident.db](file:///d:/project/Sentinel/Sentinel_level8/Sentinel_Level8_Enterprise%20-%20Copy/incident.db)): SOAR incident tracking
- **TimescaleDB** (PostgreSQL): Time-series metrics storage
- **Redis**: Message bus (Pub/Sub), caching, state storage

